tip.text: No food & drinks here other than a soft drinks vending machine. Carpark is free if you drive through the gate. Locked at night and guarded by policemen.
There isn't outdoor seating during the winter months but the view of Kaunas and of the sunset is amazing. I love this bar. Voleas Engelman draft beer served here is also really good :)
The Melaka naan and mango lassi are to die for!
This is an amazing place. Very clean hotel with great service and spacious rooms. Cute jacuzzi pool in the well-manicured garden too. Breakfast is served al fresco in the garden. Very helpful owner.
